import React from 'react'
import {Box, Center, ChakraProvider, Divider, Text, Stack} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Center>
                <Box w="1364px">
                    <Divider mt="100px" />
                </Box>
            </Center>
            <Stack>
                <Box></Box>
                <Box>
                    <Stack>
                        <Box>
                            
                        </Box>
                        <Box>
                            
                        </Box>
                    </Stack>
                </Box>
            </Stack>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Footer
